user_query: I'm planning a vacation and I want to explore different pageant contests around the world. Can you find me some interesting winners from various countries? Additionally, provide me with the airport information in Los Angeles to plan my travel.

TaskList.description: Research and compile a list of prominent beauty pageants held internationally and their recent winners.
Gather information on the winners' profiles, including their countries and achievements.
Find the airport information for Los Angeles, including location, terminals, and available airlines.
